commands to be run for executing:

- make
-./sample2D


Keyboard Controls:
	A: rotate canon above
	B: Rotate canon below
	F: increase speed
	S: Reduce speed

	up arrow  : zoom in
	down arrow : zoom out
	spacebar to shoot
	left arrow : pan left
	right arrow : pan right

Mouse Controls:

	scroll up : zoom in
	scroll down : zoom out
	right click and drag right : pan left
	right click and drag left : pan right

balls disappear on collision
score displayed on terminal
can shoot only once either the ball rolls out of window or stops due to friction.

3 targets.
1 point per target
